  "text": "We thus decompose the problem into a subproblem and a master problem. The subproblem is a mixed-integer program with bilinear constraints that optimizes profit over inventory transfers and store closings subject to a fixed markdown schedule and specific assumptions. The master problem searches for the markdown schedule that maximizes the objective value of the subproblem. This relaxation is in the spirit of the fourth heuristic considered by [CITATION_1] , which also separates pricing and inventory decisions. We start with the subproblem.",
